  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then the-- we were-- we were-- not our-- the Berihah was supposed to be none-- no preferential parties.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were for everybody.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So, these-- they were going to bring these people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were supposed to pick 'em up on the railway station in Salzburg.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So, everybody was afraid to go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I say, OK.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I'm not afraid to go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I'll go.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I'll meet him in there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So, OK.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Wear the uniform in there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I remember, [INAUDIBLE] we had a Austrian driver.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "His name was [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Hansel. ?]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we had a big truck, like a huge [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a-- a Czechoslovakian-- Tatra was the name of the truck.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was like a cattle truck, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I pull up in there, for the railroad station.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And these big [? hills ?] are coming in there, and they're [? start ?] and this.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I says, listen, I said, don't start any trouble.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because otherwise you're gonna sit in here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I say, you go in to the truck.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We're gonna take you to Camp [?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Mill. ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "At ?] that time, there was Camp [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Mill. ?] I mean, we, in Salzburg, we had three, actually we had three camps.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was Camp [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Mill, ?] I, and Camp [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Biyalik ?] So three different--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, anyhow, they went up in the truck.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I look on this little girl.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She was a cute little girl.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She caught my eye.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So, and these guys [? that ?] were [? giving ?] her, I says, OK.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So, I tell-- I saw her.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was a real hot day.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Real hot.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I tell the guy, I says, I tell to the driver, I says, listen.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Pull away from there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It's too hot in there.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
